This package is a Swift rewrite of `okmain`, originally created by Dan Groshev
and published at:

https://github.com/si14/okmain

The implementation in this repository ports the public behavior and algorithmic
approach of the upstream project into a Swift Package for Apple platforms.

Upstream `okmain` is distributed under a dual license:

- Apache License 2.0
- MIT License

This repository includes both upstream license texts in `LICENSE-APACHE` and
`LICENSE-MIT` and is distributed under the same licensing model.
